The paper discusses the robustness of multiplex networks, which can be applied to various systems such as transportation networks, social networks, and economic networks. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
